product>>description: For total concealment and game-stalking quiet construction, look no further than our Traditional Hydration Pack. Incorporating low-nap poly tricot with PVC backing, this 70-oz.-capacity pack features comfort shoulder straps and a low-profile design. Taste-free hydration-tube system. External zippered pocket and shock-cord cargo panel. Imported.

Long, challenging hunting trips require you to be prepared for any obstacle you might encounter. With Cabela's-exclusive Badlands' Release Day Pack, you'll have the pocket space, support and carry capabilities you need to be just that – prepared. The legendary Air-Track™ Suspension system combines with the technical, ultralight construction to deliver easy mobility for long treks over the most rugged terrain. Made of super-quiet KXO-32 fabric with rugged Hypalon- and Kevlar-reinforced stress points for durability that stands up to years of use in the field, it also offers a multitude of pockets - five to be exact - that team up to keep all of your must-have hunting gear and accessories secure while you're on the move. It even boasts bow-carrying capabilities for added hands-free convenience. External bedroll and compression straps. Accepts up to a 110-oz. reservoir (sold separately). Comes with Badlands' Unconditional Lifetime Warranty. Imported.
product>>name: Badlands Release Day Pack – Cabela's Exclusive

product>>description: Transport your calls, ammo and other duck-hunting accessories safely and securely in Herter's Waterfowl Field Bag. A large zippered opening delivers access to the main compartment, which has an adjustable divider to separate your gear. Exterior pockets on the front, back and sides keep essentials at the ready. Adjustable shoulder strap and neoprene-wrapped handle for easy carry. Rugged 600-denier polyester fabric resists snags and tears. Imported.

You won’t find a better gear bag for a lower price. Its durable, weather-resistant 600-denier polyester construction makes it ideal for toting everything from packable rain gear to extra odds and ends. Sturdy 1-1⁄2" nylon web carry straps can be joined by a hand-friendly wrap handle. Six exterior pockets, including zippered mesh pockets on top and side, provide multiple storage and organization options. Embroidered Cabela’s logo on front pocket. Imported.

You aren't content with getting just off the road. Your hunts take you deep into the woods. The last thing you need to be worried about is if you brought everything you may need. With a 1,200-cu.-in. capacity and classic, top-load rucksack design, our Top-Load Pack ensures you have ample space for carrying all of your field essentials. Mesh side pockets provide additional areas for keeping must-have items within easy reach, while internal and external zippered hood pockets secure additional gear and accessories. Padded back panel offers cushioned support for long days afield. Front of the pack features daisy-chain webbing for attaching accessories, as well as a handle to ensure convenient carry. Webbed haul loop. Rugged YKK® zippers with easy-to-grasp pulls. Durable, water-resistant construction. Imported.

Badlands' 2200 Hunting Pack put the Badlands brand on the map, and years of redesigning have made it the ideal hunting pack. KXO-32 fabric is extremely abrasion-resistant and long lasting. T-6 aircraft-grade-aluminum frame has an incredible strength-to-weight ratio. Built-in meat shelf makes packing out your trophy easier. Capable of holding either a bow or a rifle so you're free to use your hands. Flexible, high-strength Hypalon® and Arimid threads are used in high-stress areas for over-the-top reinforcement. Spotting-scope pocket keeps your glass protected when traveling over rough terrain. Able to carry a rifle, bow and even a pistol Imported.

With three main compartments and two pockets, the Badlands Pursuit Day Pack boasts enough room for your essential gear. Ultrastrong KX032 and nylon construction sports a waterproof urethane shell that protects your gear from moisture and remains whisper-quiet in the field. Triple-stitched seams, DuPont™ Kevlar® bartacking and Hypalon® panels ensure lasting durability. Ideal for on-the-move bowhunting with a 105-oz. hydration reservoir, sold separately. Imported.

Have all your hunting gear organized and within easy access inside our All-Day Transporter, a versatile fanny pack designed with all the features necessary for day-long excursions. The pack is constructed of silent, durable and weatherproof CT450 Plus fabric making it an obvious choice for all hunting situations. An adjustable compression pod extends from the bottom of the pack and attaches to the top of the main compartment with two side-release buckles. It's the ideal place to store extra gear such as clothing, rattling antlers and other bulky items. When not in use, the pod can be rolled and stored out of the way in the hook-and-loop pouch on the bottom of the main compartment. Molded-foam back panel and waistbelt comfortably distributes the weight of heavy loads. Front pocket contains an organizer panel and multiple elastic loops to hold scents, calls and knives. Main compartment has five internal mesh pouches to organize gear. Knife/mini-flashlight pouch on outside of main compartment keeps often-used items within quick reach. Holster-compatible waistbelt. Detachable shoulder harness. Imported.

Badlands' Treestand Day Pack is perfect for those who hunt from a treestand. Designed to carry a quiver (not included) or a bow or rifle. Hang this camouflaged, space-saving pack on a nearby limb and you're set for the day. Made from extremely durable and quiet KXO-32 fabric. Holds a 105-oz. hydration reservoir (not included). Two main compartments with a foldout stand organizer and six pockets keep all your gear organized. Imported.

Eberlestock's Team Elk Pack was designed with the serious elk hunter in mind. Integrated bow and rifle carriers for hands-free hunting, no matter the season. Intex tubular aluminum frame comfortably supports heavy loads and doubles as a haul frame. Grapple-compression straps securely hold excess gear or clothes. Hip-belt rangefinder pocket keeps your rangefinder within easy reach. Full-depth spotting-scope pocket holds most spotting scopes. NT-7 waterproof, microfleece shell is extremely quiet and sports waterproof external zippers. Breathable mesh back keeps you cool on hot days. Hydration-system compatible. Imported.

Simple and functional, the Cabela's-exclusive Badlands' Axis Hunting Pack keeps your mind on the hunt. AirTrack™ Suspension allows air to flow between your back and the pack, keeping you cool. Constructed of waterproof KXO-32 fabric with Hypalon® reinforcements for exceptional durability. Top-loading main compartment and ample pockets make it easy to organize your gear. Hydration compatible. Backed by a manufacturer's unconditional lifetime warranty. Imported.
product>>name: Badlands Axis Hunting Pack – Cabela's Exclusive

product>>description: Our Outfitter Series Deluxe Whitetail Hunting Fanny Pack offers superior hunting performance. It is constructed of durable, ultrasoft CTS 450 Tricot for silence in any condition. This Cabela’s-exclusive fabric’s shell is finished with a waterproof coating and lined with a waterproof-rated, puncture-resistant fabric. Heavy-duty zippers have cord pulls instead of noisy metal tabs. Large main compartment measures 9-1/2"H x 12"W x 4-1/2"D, with an outside zippered 8" x 9" flat map pocket. Cinch-top water-bottle pocket (water bottle not included). Padded hip belt and molded-foam back for extra comfort. Reinforced stitching at all stress points. Imported.

Built for quick, on-the-go hunts, Cabela's Stalker Sling Pack can be adjusted to sling over either shoulder. It's crafted of ultratough 600-denier CT450 polyester tricot for quiet movement and season after season of use. Adjustable shoulder sling and three-point waistband allow you to customize the pack for optimal comfort. Main pocket has five internal organizer pockets and a key fob. Shock-corded panel holds jacket or gloves. Padded back panel allows air to circulate, keeping you cool and dry on tough hikes. YKK® zippers with deluxe U-pulls. Imported.

Keep your gear at the ready with Herter's Seven-Pocket Fanny Pack. The quiet yet durable CT450 high-count tricot shell with a low-nap finish is backed with a water-repellent polyurethane lamination for reliable outdoor use. With seven zippered pockets, you can efficiently organize your necessities using the pack's 400 cu. in. of cargo space. Nylon web belt has an adjustable quick-release buckle. Imported.

From the triple-stitched seams boasting the durability of aramid thread to the DuPont™ Kevlar® bartacking and CSM panels at all major stress points, the ruggedly designed Badlands Monster Fanny Pack withstands the rigors of the most intense hunts. KX0-32™ fabric combines an ultrastrong nylon foundation with a waterproof urethane shell for superior protection from wet weather, while remaining quiet for reliable hunting performance. Flex-frame suspension transfers weight toward the hips and alleviates sag caused by heavy loads. Thermo-molded memory-foam hip belt distributes the load around the hip bone instead of placing the weight on top of it. Quick-release, yoke-style shoulder harness displaces stress evenly at the shoulders and tucks away in its own convenient pocket when not in use. Six additional storage pockets provide ample room for all your must-have gear. Features include two fold-down workstation pockets with an extra 245 cu. in. of capacity and lashing straps perfect for securing your rainwear, bedroll and other essentials to the outside. Manufacturer's unconditional lifetime warranty. Imported.

When your hunting party sets up camp deep in the backcountry, take along the Midland Outfitter Quad Pack for crystal-clear reception, transmission and sound quality from up to 38 miles away. All four radios feature 36 channels with 14 extra channels and 122 privacy codes that eliminate interference. Channel-scan feature monitors activity over all channels, and Midland's Weather Alert technology keeps you on top of any drastic changes in the weather. Hi/low power option lets you maximize range or conserve the battery. Silent mode works with headphones (not included) or eVOX with variable voice sensitivity adds hands-free use. Battery meter with low-battery indicator. Rapid Charge charges batteries in less than three hours. Water-resistant radios come equipped with a headphone jack, keystroke tones and roger beep. Pack includes: four radios, eight rechargeable battery packs, a micro-USB charging cable, USB Y-cable, car charger, AC wall adapter, desktop charger and four headsets. Manufacturer's limited three-year warranty.

With the navigational capabilities of a 12-parallel-channel GPS and the reliable communication power of a 22-channel GMRS/FRS radio, this 100% waterproof GPS/radio units let you travel anywhere with complete confidence. Channels 1-7 are FRS/GMRS, 8-14 are FRS and 15-22 are GMRS for a wide range of communication options. Each channel has 38 squelch codes for semiprivate conversation. The patent-pending peer-to-peer positioning “beams” your location to another Rino user. The FCC allows the use of GMRS channels for this Garmin-exclusive feature, which shows the receiving party the distance and bearing from your position to theirs. Powered by a rechargeable lithium-ion pack with 14 hours of run time (included) or optional AA battery pack (not included).

Communicate in the field or from your vehicle with the Midland 2-in-1 40-Channel Handheld CB Radio. This versatile CB can be used as a handheld or converted to a mobile radio with the included vehicle adapter and external antenna (not included). 4-watt power output provides a strong signal. Squelch control eliminates unwanted background noise. Built-in ANL improves reception for a weak received signal. High/low switch easily adjusts power usage for long or short range to conserve battery life. NOAA weather radio gives you instant access to weather/hazard information. Channel 9 and 19 provide access to emergency and road information. Easy-to-read backlit LCD screen displays 18 functions/modes. Keypad lock prevents accidental activation. Flexible, removable antenna with BNC connector. Plug-and-play right out of the box. Powered by six AA batteries or rechargeable batteries (not included). Includes CB radio, antenna, AC adapter, DC adapter, hand strap, rechargeable battery case, belt clip and owner's manual.

It engages the trigger guard as you holster your firearm and secures it until you release using the normal drawing motion with your trigger finger alongside the holster. No snaps or straps to get in the way. Can be worn on a belt or used as a paddle holster.

An adjustable cant for either straight drop or FBI. Proprietary plastic construction is thin, durable and comfortable to wear. Partial dual sweat guard protects your sidearm. Positive-lock trigger guard prevents snagging. Adjustable retention to match your draw-pressure prefrence.

It combines the comforts of a saddle-leather backing plate with a Napa leather front for long-lasting performance. A rigid Kydex® holster pocket allows for a fast draw and easy holstering. The removable belt clips adjust to your preferred carry height and angle. Reinforced, double-stitched seams. Covered trigger for safety. Compatible with belts up to 1-3/4"W. Right-handed shooters. Made in USA.

A key component of this patented system is its spider harness, all four points of which are connected by a unique clover-shaped Flexalon™ swivel back plate and pivot independently. The result is a perfect fit, lasting comfort and freedom of movement for handgun carriers of all sizes and shapes.
